{"tid":1020620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（求助）犯咗商品說明條例，俾人起訴，bind over機率幾大","createTime":"2019-02-13T17:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T09:41:17.000Z","uid":199960,"like":8,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"800c5c103dcc71954b99be23bc8890b07f659d53","tid":1020620,"uid":199960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:09:00.000Z","msg":"小弟18歲學生，前嗰排俾人放蛇捉到賣一對假鞋，$400左右&hellip;<br />\n去我屋企搜查搵唔到野，我放上去個AC都剩係得一對鞋。<br />\n俾人起訴左，口供講咗好多野，搵咗律師幫我寫信去律政司申請不提證供起訴希望冇案底⋯⋯<br />\n好快就要上庭啦，<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請問各位巴絲小弟冇案底嘅機率有幾多？<br />\n我無犯過任何事之前。<br />\n前途盡毀，我真係擔心左好多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求求各位全能嘅巴絲打可以答我，感激不盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ae69a9d3becf17ab9c5cfd2ef900c0e0b17456","tid":1020620,"uid":199960,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:10:50.000Z","msg":"連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e74b4a052945e741b90761ad5ae99c1b8d60cf","tid":1020620,"uid":31361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:11:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">李嘉欣.jpg</span></span>"},{"pid":"7d7755e145eb3e16d269867a64f5dee8ab129d22","tid":1020620,"uid":20120,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:13:06.000Z","msg":"賣假野<br />\n應有此報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeea38666771afe05b4b3376316dbedbc765ad69","tid":1020620,"uid":37338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:13:29.000Z","msg":"賣侵權野刑事喎 罰錢留案底"},{"pid":"1857b2c9e37321448d9764ffb6c454cde49dffa2","tid":1020620,"uid":111,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab49bc439245f3efd78a0a390522170909cada3",